@base <http://example.org/> .
@prefix ont: <http://ont.example.org/> .

<http://example.org/alice> <http://example.org/ont/hasAge> 25 .
<http://example.org/bob> <http://example.org/ont/hasAge> 18 .
<http://example.org/charlie> <http://example.org/ont/hasAge> 21 .
<http://example.org/dave> <http://example.org/ont/hasAge> 30 .
<ellie> <http://example.org/ont/hasAge> 26 .
<felix> ont:hasAge 37 .
<alphabet> <http://example.org/ont/hasCount> 26 .

<http://example.org/foo> <http://ont.example.org/false> "false" .
<http://example.org/bar> <http://ont.example.org/false> "false" .
